T1  - Preference Aggregation With Incomplete Information
AU  - Chambers, Christopher P.
AU  - Hayashi, Takashi
Y1  - 2014/03/01
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA11612
